Eric was upset and said that it was all bullshit.
Howard told him to tell his mother that he loves her but around then the ph=
one went dead. The caller said that it's because you're cheating life. John=
ny said he has to get him the call so he can hear it on the air. Howard was=
 saying he might have to call into this chess show that he knows about too.=
 He said he might even call himself DABA (Da Bad Ass) like JD did online.
Johnny explained to Howard what Eric was asking for and how he was telling =
him to find this guy he had a problem with and how he  should know what to =
do from there.
He also pointed out that if he had been roasted, he might have asked to hav=
e everyone from the show hit. He said he might have to call into that show =
to talk about that. Eric said he doesn't want any harm to come to the guy a=
t all. Howard said they really don't want any harm to come to this guy Jerr=
y. Eric said ''yeah'' but it didn't sound so convincing.
9:45am Chubby Checker Calls In.
7:35am Chris Rock Visits. He eventually picked up a call and the caller sai=
d ''fuck 'em'' to Richard Jeni.
Eric said that was the first time he's done that since he was a kid. She sa=
id she's never felt so bad in her entire life after staying up with no slee=
p like that.
He ended up goofing on JD about that for a short time. 6:10am Howard tried =
to take a phone call but ended up complaining about the phone bank and how =
he couldn't read the numbers on the buttons.
Eric The Midget Godfather Asking Johnny Fratto For Favors.
They said that if that guy Jerry does end up dead or something, the cops ar=
e going to go right to Johnny because of this message.
Howard asked Eric if he has a mattress pad and found out he does.
7:35am Chubby Checker Pissed At Howard. Howard asked Eric how he explains t=
hat. Artie said he thinks there are probably more people in this country th=
an you'd think who are fucking their cats.
Robin said she tried chess over the weekend and it went horribly so she's n=
ot so sure she'd want to keep playing. Howard asked him what he says when c=
hicks ask him what that means. 9:25am Greg On Jeni And Beth O Visits.
He was also saying that he'd still like to get into that stuff with the Bat=
tlestar Galictica thing.
He thinks that Johnny misunderstood Eric and thought he was asking him to t=
ake out ''Jeni'' (Richard Jeni) and that's how that guy ended up dead.=

